title: Microsoft Office 2016 Pro Plus iso Dec 2015 - {Ranger.03}
description:
This new version, called Office 2016 on both Mac and PC, is the first to have collaboration and sharing tools that closely match what Google Docs has had for years. You can finally work with other people on a document, spreadsheet or presentation in real time, seeing what they are editing as they make changes.Microsoft also added integrations with its search engine Bing and messaging and video-calling app Skype. These welcome additions blend seamlessly into the apps and continue Office's tradition of having special extra features that it's competitors don't.
